snippet.title: Desolate Roads - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Desolate Roads on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1328620/Desolate_Roads/

Desolate Roads is a short first-person psychological horror game. Your car is out of gas in the middle of nowhere and there is nothing else around, just empty roads, a dark forest, and the endless thick and strangling fog. You have no other choice but to go and explore this seemingly abandoned place alone.
